        <h2>🌈 Jason Torchinsky [They/Them] 🌈</h2>
        <h3 class="member-role">President & Treasurer</h3>
        <p>Jason fell in love with West Coast Swing in 2022 at a local social while interning in Albuquerque, NM—and they’ve been hooked ever since. Back in Madison, WI, they poured their energy into organizing queer West Coast Swing socials through a queer graduate student group at the University of Wisconsin–Madison, helping create spaces where everyone could feel at home on the dance floor.</p>
        <p>Jason is one of the founders of ABQueer WCS, and currently serves as our President, Treasurer, and Chair of the Event Planning and Organizing Committee. They travel across the country to compete and bring high-energy hype to every event they attend.</p>
      </div>
