        <h3 class="member-role">Vice President</h3>
        <p>Sarah began West Coast Swing in 2024 and has been with ABQueer WCS since the very first event. She currently serves as the Vice President and is the Chair of the Advertising and PR commiette (AKA our social media queen). Sarah is a huge advocate for the LGBTQIA2S+ community and she is excited to help  our community grow, dance, and be seen.</p>
